
HyperGit Vim Plugin
===================


Installation
============

    $ vimana i hypergit.vim

    $ make -f Makefile.pure install


Add Git Menu key mapping to your ~/.vimrc:


    nmap <leader>g   :ToggleGitMenu<CR>


Key Mappings
============

    <leader>ci   commit current file changes
    <leader>ca   commit all changes

